                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">if its level, then level 18 (the breeze spell level) is a new threshold for increased enchanter aggro
<br />

<br />
I didnt see increased aggro (to start using blink) until I had the spell breeze
<br />
(which you receive at the tail end of level 18)
<br />

<br />
I thought blink was worthless when I got it (at 16) but now due to the weird aggro at 18+, im constantly using blink
<br />

<br />
I think aggro is more likely related to using clarity/haste buffs
<br />
- but I'm only guessing
<br />

<br />
I have seen *big aggro* if I cast group haste on mob pull</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://wow.allakhazam.com/profile.html?15649" target="_blank" class="postlink"> Sharlene </a> WoW level 42 Priest, Whisperwind server
