                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">To the monsters, you're all part of a Group encounter so you get aggro if anyone else in your group gets aggro.  A solution is to get out of range; Cry for Help and Sprint away.
<br />

<br />
Monsters consider Breeze to be a heal, which it is if you think about it (Power over Time).  That's why you're getting intense aggro for it.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Juneau, Human Fury/27 and Provisioner/34 of Freeport (EQ2/Crushbone)
<br />
Currahee, Erudite Shaman/14 and Alchemist/21 of Freeport (EQ2/Crushbone)</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
