                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I did notice something helpful was to have the MA engage and pull the mobs only maybe halfway back. Then ae aggro, then I would come up and melee/heal/debuff/nuke whatever. I rarely have pulled aggro off of him handling situations this way - unless I move to another mob inadvertantly <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile.gif" border="0" /> Then sometimes they get pissy at me <img src="images/smiles/icon_wink.gif" alt="icon_wink.gif" border="0" />
