                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The Fighter AE taunt ability is a green (single group AE), not a blue (multi-group PBAoE) effect.  It is true the range is rather short, so even though you can't use it to agro more than one group, it is possible that elements of that group will be out of range of the taunt if used for pulling.  What ever the best method to lock agro against non-concentration based buffs is a learning process every tank and group needs to develop.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
